<br>
1) Air ele form- although nice for resists, levitate is not allowed in so many zones that it makes this aa of very limited usefulness.  Look into water form (FT1) or Earth form (HP).<br>
<br>
2) Suspend Minion-- this is simply THE BEST AA a mage can get.  Well SM2 is at least, also note that you need no pre-reqs for this so once you get to the appropriate level (63 or 4 cant remember) you can crank out the 8 points and get it.  You cannot zone with it, that kills the pet no matter what.  It is great for invissing and even better for Pet canni!  Hit suspend minion (4 sec cast time) to hide your good pet then chain cast/reclaim your MS2/lvl 49 earth pet for approximatly FT100 mana regen.  I am so in love with this I cannot tell you how good it is.<br>
<br>
Edit: SM2 also <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>resets the enrage timer</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> and heals your pet each cycle for the amount of +hp gear you have on him.  For example, if you have girdle + weapons each time you suspend/unsuspend your pet heals +600 hp !!<br>
<br>
<br>
Look into SCM and Pet Discipline ASAP as well, both very awesome abilities.<br>
<br>
Good hunting Kim!<br>
